snippet.title: Roboquest - Coming to Playstation
snippet.description:
Roboquest will be coming to Playstation in the first half of 2025.

Wishlist it on the Playstation Store here: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10010255

Roboquest is a fast-paced shooter with Roguelite set in a vivid futureworld.

Jump into the steel shoes of a steel Guardian, alone or in 2-players coop and save mankind.

Get it now!
Steam | https://store.steampowered.com/app/692890/Roboquest/
Gamepass | https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/roboquest/9p47s7njgwzl
Epic Game Store | https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/roboquest-9ad17a

Join the community!
Discord | Discord.gg/Roboquest
X (Twitter) | https://twitter.com/RoboquestGame
TikTok | https://www.tiktok.com/@roboquestgame
